{
  "stem": "20021.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She declared all the Judenrats to be traitors and collaborators of the worst kind.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So that's her opinion.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She might be right, she might not be right.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "On the other hand, the people in the Judenrat claimed, look, under the circumstances, we did some good.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Now, the kind of good they did obviously was of the nature that they selected the people who were resettled.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So if they selected, say, older people, they clearly helped [INAUDIBLE] younger people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I-- I don't know how to react to that or how judge that, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But they claimed that if it weren't for them, things would have been much worse.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Their function was usually A, to enforce order.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They had the full authority as far as the Jews were concerned.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "B, the Germans would every once in a while say, you have to collect $10,000, you have to collect the kilogram of gold or whatever, and they would extract that money from-- from the people, you know, and deliver it to the Germans.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And that would stave off the day of reckoning and so forth.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But people not in large numbers were constantly killed just on the spot by any German gestapo men who would arrive in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They did that just to spread fear, to keep the people scared all the time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't see, but you heard of it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I know for-- know intimately about this case of-- of [?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Bella ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Weisberg, ?] who was a friend of mine was a girl who was very beautiful.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And suddenly a German came into just the square there and picks her up and takes her and shoots her.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that's one case, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
